title: Trump says he was 'amazed that Harvey Weinstein got scholnged'
description: Donald Trump, during an interview on the Dan Bongino Show, discussed how he was surprised Harvey Weinstein faced severe punishment despite being backed by Democrats. Trump referred to Weinstein as the 'king of the woke' and said Democrats typically protect their own. “But boy — you don’t know him well, I don’t know him well, but I watched that and it was amazing. So when they do get hit, they get hit. But that’s the only one I can think of, normally they protect everybody,” he continued. “What they did was Adams, I think, is very suspect.”
author: TOI World Desk

title: Are Meghan and Harry buying a house in Portugal? King Charles has a message
description: Royal experts are also aware that Harry and Meghan are buying a house in Portugal and they believe that King Charles' message to them would be of indifference. King Charles is not going to "concern himself" with the news, experts claimed. King Charles evicted them from their Windsor property after they left the family and defamed the family in the public but the King will not be perturbed by the news.
